Memo

Yasuo Nagao                    07.03.2011  02:44:08
Hello,

After talk with customer, I tried to test more with Designer 8.2,
I could reproduce problem with Designer standalone also.

Problem description:
   After several operation on Design view, Designer will be crashed.

   It does not matter for with/wihtout embedding SAPGUI.

Environment:
   SAP tested environment: WinXP SP-3 + Reader X

How to reproduce
   Start Designer 8.2 (8.2.3.5112.1.653984).
   Open attached xdp file.
BODY->HDLUNIT_TF->HDL_UNIT_DATA->HDL_UNIT_CONTENT
   Under this subform, click field quickly many times on design view.
   Refer to attached PDF file (HowToReproduce.pdf).
   In order to reproduce problem, it is necessary to do several times.
   -> Designer will be crashed.

Expected from Adobe Support
   Reproduce same problem with Adobe and provide fix of Designer.

Best regards,
Yasuo
