Short Text

Line details cannot be edited.
________________________________________________________________________

System

Client          64
Release
System          9.0
________________________________________________________________________

Message Attributes

Processor       Harvey Xu
Priority        Medium
Language        E
Status          Confirmed
Component       SBO-PUR-REC
________________________________________________________________________

Technical information
Test Plan Title      SAP Business One 9.0 New Features
Test Package Title   General Issues
Test Case Name       GENERALISSUES
Test Case Title      General Issues

Describe your procedure in detail

1.create a GRPO with two lines
2.right click against the first line and select Row Details
3.try to go through the lines and update qty fileds on Row
Details screen

expected:

User can go through the lines by click up/down icon. And qty
fields can be updated.

actual:
Not all the qty fields in the lines can be changed. And the document
line number on GRPO screen will disappear after
clicking up/down icon. Please refer to the attach.
________________________________________________________________________

Memo

Yangming Wu                    04.04.2012  21:41:15
I checked this issue and found out this is a common bug for the other
type of document. And the reason is not caused by the changing value of
qty, just click up/down icon and then click some of the column, this
phenomenon will happen.
Suggestion:Check the file of __GRID_EXL.c, notice this line:
grid->SetValue (item.GetColumn(), *curRow, grt_Vis, formatStr, false, tr
ue); When the column num equal zero, the value of formatStr is empty.
________________________________________________________________________

